Description: This project shows the use of linked data to provide a way to represent and consume information about unmissing people retrieved from non-governamental organization's sites. A tool was created to mark as spam messages about unmissing people on Facebook- using a database that implements the linked data principles.
Sources: Web:http://desaparecidos.ice.ufjf.br/ Name:Adriano Delvoux; Jairo Francisco de Souza Email:jairo.souza@ice.ufjf.br
